OL,3,CWales drawn to face England in 2027
OL,4,CRugby World Cup as group finalised
OL,6,FWales and England will clash in the
OL,7,Fgroup stage of the 2027 men's Rugby
OL,8,FWorld Cup.
OL,10,FThe two nations were both named in
OL,11,FPool F for the expanded tournament in
OL,12,FAustralia, which for the first time
OL,13,Fwill feature 24 teams.
OL,15,FWales and England are joined by Tonga
OL,16,Fand Zimbabwe, while Ireland and
OL,17,FScotland will meet in Pool D along
OL,18,Fwith Uruguay and Portugal.
