OL,4,CRugby World Cup as group finalised
OL,6,FHosts Australia missed out on being
OL,7,Famong the top six teams in pot one and
OL,8,Fpaid the price when they were paired
OL,9,Fwith rivals New Zealand in Pool A.
OL,11,FDebutants Hong Kong face a baptism of
OL,12,Ffire in the same group along with
OL,13,FChile, while two-time defending
OL,14,Fchampions South Africa are in Pool B
OL,15,Fwith Italy, Georgia and Romania.
OL,17,FFrance head Pool E, which also
OL,18,Fincludes Japan, while Argentina and
OL,19,FFiji are in Pool C.
