OL,3,CWales drawn to face England in 2027
OL,4,CRugby World Cup as group finalised
OL,6,FThe tournament will take place from
OL,7,FOctober 1 to November 13, 2027. The
OL,8,Ftop two teams from each pool will
OL,9,Fadvance to the knockout stages along
OL,10,Fwith the four highest-ranked third-
OL,11,Fplaced teams.
OL,13,FThe news comes after Wales suffered a
OL,14,F73-0 defeat to South Africa at the
OL,15,FPrincipality Stadium in their final
OL,16,Fautumn international of 2025. It
OL,17,Fbecame Wales' heaviest defeat on home
OL,18,Fsoil and the first time the men's side
OL,19,Fhad failed to score a point in Cardiff
OL,20,Fsince the 1960s.
